        {
            "title": "SEC批准廢除當沖交易規則 Webull股價飆升",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Q6h6QwxW6sSH1MqrHXbmsg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA6U04V_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - Webull (NASDAQ: BULL)股價週三飆升逾9%,此前美國證券交易委員會批准對當沖交易規則進行重大改革,終結了投資者必須在孖展戶口持有至少25,000美元才能執行頻繁交易的長期要求。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">競爭對手零售券商Robinhood Markets (NASDAQ: HOOD)的股價也上漲,漲幅達5.7%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此次批准是在金融業監管局提議廢除限制之後做出的,該限制禁止資產少於25,000美元的投資者在五個交易日內進行超過四次當沖交易。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-ccf35fc5-98bb-356a-9348-ed4c54e72b3a-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據新框架,所有客戶將被要求維持足夠的權益以涵蓋其持倉的即時風險,無論帳戶規模大小。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">SEC助理秘書Sherry Haywood表示,公眾反饋\"壓倒性地支持\"這一轉變,該轉變取消了最低權益門檻和當沖交易者的正式定義。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">零售券商迅速對此舉表示歡迎。Webull集團總裁兼美國執行長Anthony Denier向Investing.com表示,\"當沖交易規則改革早就該進行了\",並補充說\"當今的散戶投資者比以往任何時候都更加知情、更加投入,並擁有更好的工具。\"</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他表示,更新規則\"是關於讓監管與市場實際運作方式保持一致,並確保准入不會受到任意限制\",並指出<span><span><span><span>Webull</span></span></span></span>一直在為這一轉變做準備,作為其更廣泛關注准入、透明度和投資者控制的一部分。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">\"我們一直在為這一轉變做準備,因為我們相信散戶投資的未來植根於准入、透明度和控制,\"Denier補充道。\"隨著市場格局的演變,我們的重點仍然是為投資者提供他們負責任交易所需的工具和見解。\"</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/sec%E6%89%B9%E5%87%86%E5%BB%A2%E9%99%A4%E7%95%B6%E6%B2%96%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E8%A6%8F%E5%89%87-webull%E8%82%A1%E5%83%B9%E9%A3%86%E5%8D%87-144744586.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-15 23:02:08",
