        {
            "title": "摩根士丹利:油價上漲可能抵消退稅增幅帶來的提振效果",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/t8H8YwWPBRcVaBSDkEjFBg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/indicatornews_1_M_1440048330.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 摩根士丹利表示,美國稅務退稅金額略低於預期,引發外界對退稅今年能為家庭支出提供多少支持的疑問。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該行經濟學家希瑟·伯格(Heather Berger)在給客戶的報告中寫道,退稅金額\"略低於我們的預期\",並補充說,該公司原本預計財政法案今年只會將消費\"提升幾個十分點\"。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">聯邦退稅金額較去年同期增長14%,略低於摩根士丹利預期的15%至25%區間。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-dcbd45c6-d492-321a-aecc-409e6efb48b1-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據稱,平均退稅金額增長11%至3,462美元,增幅較為溫和的原因是獲得退稅的納稅人數量增加。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">伯格指出,稅率目前低於去年水平,但高於該公司的預測,這意味著\"我們對2026年消費增長約20個基點的預測存在一定下行風險\"。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據該報告,更大的風險在於燃料成本上升。伯格估計,\"如果今年平均油價上漲15%(達到3.60美元或更高),將足以抵消平均退稅增加的350美元\"。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這種動態可能對中等收入家庭造成不成比例的影響,儘管低收入者獲得的退稅較少,但他們在汽油上的絕對支出也較少。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據報導,州級數據表現較為強勁,稅收徵收呈上升趨勢,預扣稅顯示高收入家庭的收入持續增長。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">但在全國層面,伯格警告稱,\"油價支出上升可能足以抵消平均退稅的增加\",從而限制政策制定者預期的整體消費提振效果。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%91%A9%E6%A0%B9%E5%A3%AB%E4%B8%B9%E5%88%A9-%E6%B2%B9%E5%83%B9%E4%B8%8A%E6%BC%B2%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E6%8A%B5%E6%B6%88%E9%80%80%E7%A8%85%E5%A2%9E%E5%B9%85%E5%B8%B6%E4%BE%86%E7%9A%84%E6%8F%90%E6%8C%AF%E6%95%88%E6%9E%9C-134016997.html",
